    <item>
      <title>英国关闭俄罗斯加密货币富豪网络，转移寡头数十亿美元资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/crypto-rich-russian-networks-moving-oligarch-billions-shut-down-by-uk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国警方表示，他们已经关闭了俄罗斯网络，该网络通过在欧洲、中东和南美洲交换现金和加密货币，为寡头、街头帮派和间谍转移数十亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/crypto-rich-russian-networks-moving-oligarch-billions-shut-down-by-uk</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 15:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
